\id PHM
\h BILIMUNGU DHÄWU BOLWUŊ (PHILEMON)
\toc3 Bilimun
\toc2 Bilimungu dhäwu bolwuŋ
\toc1 BOLWUŊ DJORRA' DJUY'YUNAWUY BILIMUNGU NITJIMATJKALAŊUWUY
\mt1 BOLWUŊ DJORRA' DJUY'YUNAWUY BILIMUNGU NITJIMATJKALAŊUWUY
\imt1 Dhuwal nhe dhu ŋurruŋuny nhäma
\ip Bolyu gan dhuwandja djorra' wukirri beŋur dharruŋguŋur yolŋuwal yäkuwal Bilimungal, ŋunhi ŋayi ḻundu'mirriŋu nhanŋu. Ga dhuwaliyi Bilimundja yolŋu ḻukunydja' mirithirr, yurr ŋayi ŋunhi Garraywalaŋumirr yulŋuny, ga dharrwa ŋayi gan yolŋuny walalany ŋayathaŋal ḏapmaranhawuynhan walalany, ŋunhi walal ŋuli ganha ŋunhiliyiny wäŋaŋurnydja nhanukal buku-ḻuŋ'maranhaminyan buku-ŋal'yunarawnha God-Waŋarrwun.
\ip Ga wukirriny ŋayi dhuwal djorrany' guŋga'yun ga ŋunha wiripuny yolŋuny yäkuny Nitjimatjnha. Nitjimatjtja dhuwal yolŋu ḏapmaranhawuy djämamirr nhanŋu Bilimungu, yurr ŋayi nhanukal ŋunhi bili waṉḏirr winya'yun, nhakun ŋayi romnhan bakmaraŋal. Ga gulŋiyinany maṉḏa gan ŋunhi Nitjimatjtja ga Bolnydja rrambaŋi yan dharruŋguŋurnydja. Ga beŋuryiny dhurrwaraŋur bala ŋayi Nitjimatjtja walŋan-gurrupanmirr Garraywala, bala ŋayi ḻundu'thirra Bolwuny ga guŋga'yunamirra ŋayi nhanŋu. Manymak, ga ŋayiny ŋunhi Bolyuny wukirri djorrany' nhanŋuny Bilimunguny waŋan ŋayi ga ŋanya ŋayi dhu yakan mari-bunany maḏakarritjthirrnydja nhanŋuny Nitjimatjkuny, yänan ŋayi dhu bäy-lakaraman nhanŋu ga gumurr-ŋamathirra bili ŋayi ŋunhi Garraywun nhakun malthunamirr.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Dhuwandja djorra' ŋarrakuŋ Bolwuŋ,\f * \fr 1:1 \ft Paul\f* ŋunhi ŋarra ga dhuwal nhinany dharruŋguŋur bili ŋarra ŋuli ga dhäwu lakaram Djesu-Christkalaŋuwuy, ga wiripuny dhuwal Dimithiwuŋ\f * \fr 1:1 \ft Timothy\f* muka, ŋunhi ŋayi limurruŋ wäwa Garraywalaŋumirr. Yurr nhuŋu dhuwal yulŋuny Bilimun\f * \fr 1:1 \ft Philemon\f* dhäwuny ŋunhi nhe linyalaŋ ḻundu marrkapmirr, ga rrambaŋi limurr ga nhakun djäma Garraywu.
\v 2 Yo. Ga walalaŋguny ŋarra ga dhuwal djuy'yundhi märr-ŋamathinyawuy ŋurikiwurruŋguny yolŋuw walalaŋ Garraywalaŋumirriwnydja mala ŋunhi walal ŋuli ga buku-ḻuŋ'thun ga buku-ŋal'yun nhokal wäŋaŋur. Ga wiripuny ŋarra ga dhuwal djuy'yun märr-ŋamathinyawuy limurruŋgalaŋaw Garraywalaŋumirriw yapaw yäkuw Yäpiw,\f * \fr 1:2 \ft Apphia\f* ga wiripuny wäwaw limurruŋgalaŋaw Yätjipatjku,\f * \fr 1:2 \ft Archippus\f* ŋunhi ŋayi ŋuli ga djäma yan bitjan bili gumurr-wuṉḏaŋarrwurr romgurr Garraywu gulyunamiriw.
\p 
\v 3 Ga dhuwal ŋarra ga bukumirriyaman nhumalaŋ Garraywalaŋumirriwnydja, märr ŋayi dhu limurruŋgal God-Waŋarryuny Bäpaynydja ga Garrayyuny Djesu-Christthuny gurrupanna nhumalany nhanŋuwuy ŋayi mel-wuyunawuynydja ga mägayany rom.
\s1 Bilimungu märr-ŋamathinyawuy ga märr-yuwalkthinyawuy
\s2 Philemon's love and faith
\sr Bilimun 4-7
\p 
\v 4-5 Wäwa ŋarraku Bilimun,\f * \fr 1:4-5 \ft Philemon\f* bili muka ŋarra ŋäkulnydja nhokalaŋuwuynydja, ŋunhi nhe ŋuli ga märr-ŋamathirr God-Waŋarrwalaŋawnydja yolŋuw walalaŋ bukmakkun yan, ga ŋunhi nhe ŋuli ga märr-yuwalkthirr nhanŋu Garraywu Djesuw. Ga bitjan bili ŋarra ŋuli ga dhuwal bukumirriyamany yan nhuŋu, bala ŋarra ŋuli yan buku-gurrpanna ŋanya God-Waŋarrnhany nhokalaŋuwuynydja.
\v 6 Ŋunhi limurr ŋuli ga märr-yuwalkthinyamirrnydja mala nhina waŋganyŋurnydja, ga guŋga'yunmirrnydja marrtji bala-räli'yunmirrnydja, ŋunhiyiny limurr ŋuli yuwalknha yan dharaŋandja bukmak nhä malany ŋunhi ŋayi God-Waŋarryu gurrupar limurruŋ. Yo, ga ŋarrany ŋuli ga dhuwal bukumirriyaman nhumalaŋ, märr nhumany dhu ga ŋunhi mirithirra yänan galkiwatjnha nhinany waŋgany-manapanminyawuynha Djesu-Christnha.
\v 7 Marrkapmirr wäwa ŋarraku, ŋäkul muka ŋarra ŋunhi dhäwuny' nhokalaŋuwuy, ŋunhi nhaltjarr nhe gan märr-ŋamathin Garraywalaŋumirriw yolŋuw walalaŋ, bala yan nhe gan guŋga'yurra walalany. Ga dhiyaŋiyiny dhuwal dhäwuy ŋarranhawuynhany mirithinan nhakun galŋa-djulŋithinyamaraŋal, ga guŋga'yurra, ŋayaŋu-rur'maraŋala manapar. Ga wiripuny nhe gan ŋunhi ŋayaŋu-yal'maraŋal walalany bukmaknha yan Godkalaŋumirriny yolŋuny walalany dhiyaliyi.
\s1 Bolyu ŋäŋ'thurr Bilimunnha Nitjimatjku
\s2 Paul's request to Philemon about Onesimus
\sr Bilimun 8-22
\p 
\v 8 Yo Bilimun,\f * \fr 1:8 \ft Philemon\f* ŋarra nhuŋu dhuwal wäwa'mirriŋu Djesu-Christkalaŋumirr, ga dhunupa dhuwal ŋarraku ŋarra balaŋ nhuŋu gurrupul ḏälnydja dhäruk; ŋunhi balaŋ ŋarra nhuŋu biyakiyiny waŋi, märr balaŋ nhe ŋunhiyiny yan märraŋun ŋarrany dhäruktja.
\v 9 Yurr yaka ŋarra dhu bitjandhiny nhirrpan nhuŋu rom. Ŋarrany nhuŋu ga dhuwal märr-ŋamathirr, bala ŋarra dhu yänan ŋäŋ'thuna nhuna gurrum'thuna. Ga marŋgi muka nhe ŋarraku ŋunhi ŋarrany dhuwal Bol,\f * \fr 1:9 \ft Paul\f* yurr worruŋun ŋarra dhuwal yulŋuny, ga dhiyaŋuny bala ŋarra ga dhuwal nhina dharruŋguŋura, bili ŋarra ŋuli ganha ŋunhi dhäwu lakaranha nhanukalaŋuwuy Djesu-Christkalaŋuwuy. Ga nhepin dhu guyaŋany ga mala-djarr'yundja nhaltjan nhe dhu djäma.
\v 10 Ga dhuwanna ŋarra ga ŋäŋ'thunna nhuna Nitjimatjkuny,\f * \fr 1:10 \ft Onesimus (Nitjimatjtja yäku dhuwal mayali' ‘djäma-manymakmirr’)\f* ŋunhi ŋayiny balanya nhakun ŋarraku gäthu'mirriŋun Djesu-Christkalnydja yäkuy. Ŋunhi nhakun ŋarra gan dhiyal nhinan dharruŋguŋur, balanyamirriynha ŋarra nhanŋu ŋunhi bäpathinany, bili ŋayi ŋunhi märr-yuwalkthinany Garraywuny ŋarrakalaŋuwurra.
\v 11 Yurr ŋäthilnydja ŋayi nhuŋuny ganha yaka warray djäma-manymakkunha, yan ŋayi waṉḏinan nhokal. Yurr dhiyaŋuny bala ŋayi nhuŋu dhuwali manymaknha djämamirrnydja, ga balanyayi bili ŋayi dhuwali ŋarrakuny djäma-manymakmirryi.
\p 
\v 12 Ga dhuwanna ŋarra ga djuy'yunna roŋanmaraman ŋanya Nitjimatjnhany nhokalnha, yurr ŋayaŋumirr ŋayi dhuwali yulŋuny marrtjinany ŋarrakalaŋumirr.
\v 13 Ŋarrany ga dhuwal baḏak yan gärri dharruŋguŋur, manymakpuynydja dhäwupuy lakaranhawuy nhanukalaŋuwuynydja Djesu-Christkalaŋawuynydja. Ga djälthinany ŋarra gan ŋunhi nhanŋu Nitjimatjkuny, ŋayi balaŋ ganha dhiyal yan banydji nhinanha ŋarrakal, märr balaŋ ŋayi ŋarrany ganha guŋga'yuna dhiyal nhokal dharapulŋur.
\v 14 Bitjan ŋarra ga dhuwal guyaŋany nhanŋu gam. Ŋarra dhu ga yakan ŋanya ŋayatham wiyindja dhiyalnydja, bili nhe mak ga dhuwaliyi djälthirr nhanŋu dhiyaliyiny. Bala ŋarra ga dhuwal roŋanmaraman ŋanya nhokal. Ga beŋuryiny nhe dhu nhepin yan guyaŋa ga mala-djarr'yun nhaltjan nhe dhu djäma nhanŋu. Ga ŋuli nhe djäl, nhe dhu ŋanya roŋanmaraman rälin ŋarrakun guŋga'yunaraw. Yurr yaka ŋarra dhu nhuna dhar'thar-gurrupandja nhanŋu.
\p 
\v 15 Nhä mak ŋunhiyiny God-Waŋarrwuŋun dhukarr nhanŋu, nhokalaŋaw bäyimbuywuny djämamirriw Nitjimatjkuny, ŋunhi ŋayi ganarrthaŋalnydja nhunany märr gurriri, märr ŋayi dhu märr-yuwalkthirr Djesu-Christku, ga dhäŋur beŋuryiny ŋayi dhu roŋiyirryi nhokal goŋlil, märr nheny dhu ga ŋayathamany ŋanya wiyinŋumirra.
\v 16 Yo, baḏak yan ŋayi nhuŋu dhuwali ḏapmaranhawuynydja djämamirr, yurr yaka nhe dhu ŋanya ga mirithirrnydja guyaŋa ŋunhi ŋayi nhuŋu dhuwali ḏapmaranhawuynydja djämamirr yan. Ŋany dhiyaŋuny bala ŋayi dhuwali nhuŋu wäwan marrkapmirra Djesu-Christkalaŋuwurra. Ŋarrakalnydja ŋayi dhuwali marrkapmirra dhika mirithirra. Yurr nheny dhu ga ŋunhi märr-ŋamathirrnydja ga marrkapthundja nhanŋu bulun dhika, bili ŋayi nhunany dhu gi guŋga'yurrnydja ŋunhi nhakun märrma'ŋura dhukarrŋurnydja, waŋganydja ŋayi nhuŋu bäyimbuy djämamirr, ga waŋganydja ŋayi nhuŋu wäwa'mirriŋun Garraywalaŋumirra.
\v 17 Yo, ŋaliny muka dhuwal yuwalk yan ŋayaŋu-gurruṯumirrnydja maṉḏa litjalaŋguwuy. Buku-djulŋi, gumurr-ŋamathiny gi nhanŋu Nitjimatjkuny mirithi yan ŋini, biyak bili yan nhakun nhe balaŋ ŋunhi ŋarraku gumurr-ŋamathi, ŋuli balaŋ ŋarra nhunany gumurr-guwatjmulnydja.
\v 18 Ga ŋuli ŋayi nhuŋu ŋula nhä djäma yätjkurr ŋäthilnydja, ga wiripuny mak ŋayi ŋula djaw'yurr nhokalaŋuŋur ŋula nhä, yänan lakaraŋun ŋarrakal nhä ŋayi märraŋal.
\v 19 Ga dhuwanna gay'yi yulŋuny, ŋarra ga wukirrin ŋarrapinyan ŋarra yäkun ŋunhi. Ŋarra dhu Bolyu\f * \fr 1:19 \ft Paul\f* yuwalknha yan buku-roŋanmaramany nhuŋuny. “Yurr ŋarrany nhuna dhu yan waŋa guyaŋanhamirriyam, ŋunhi nheny walŋathin ga märraŋal Garraynha ŋarrakalaŋawurr. Yaka ŋunhiyiny moŋu.”
\v 20 Yo, wäwa ŋarraku Djesu-Christkalaŋumirr, ŋaliny ŋayaŋu rur'maranhamirra Garraywala yan. Buku-djulŋi, nheny dhu bäy-lakaraman nhanŋu Nitjimatjkuny,\f * \fr 1:20 \ft Onesimus\f* ga ŋulawitjandhiny nhakun ŋunhi, ŋarranhany nhe dhu ŋunhi ŋayaŋu-manymakkuman.
\v 21 Ŋarrany ga märr-yuwalkthirra nhuŋu, ŋunhi nheny dhu ŋarrany dhäruk märraman yan. Ga dhuwanna ŋarra ga wukirrin nhuŋu bili ŋarra marŋgi nhuŋu, ŋunhi nhe dhu djäman bala yan ŋunhi nhaku ŋarra ga dhuwal ŋäŋ'thun nhuna. Ga djämany nhe dhu bulun dhika, djuḻkmaraman dhu ŋunhi nhaku ŋarra ga dhuwal ŋäŋ'thun nhuna.\fig Paul and Onesimus|src="CN02091C.tif" size="col" loc="DC" ref="Bilimun 01.18-21"\fig*
\v 22 Ga bulu waŋganygun ŋarra dhu nhuna ŋäŋ'thun. Ŋarrany ga dhuwal märr-gatjpu'yun ŋayi dhu God-Waŋarryu buku-bakmaraman nhumalaŋ bukumirriyanhawuynydja, bala roŋanmaraman ŋarranhany nhumalaŋgala. Nhämirr balaŋ nhe dhu ŋula ŋäthilmirriyaman ŋarraku dhaḻakarrnydja ŋorranharawnydja?
\s1 Dhurrwara-ḏaw'yundja ga dhuwanna dhäruk
\s2 Final words
\sr Bilimun 23-25
\p 
\v 23 Yipaparatjtja\f * \fr 1:23 \ft Epaphras\f* ŋunhi yolŋu yäku, ŋunhi ŋayi djämamirr Djesu-Christku, dhuwal ŋayi ga dharruŋguŋura gärriny ŋalinyun rrambaŋin, ga djuy'yundja ŋayi ga dhuwal nhanŋuwuy ŋayi märr-ŋamathinyawuynha nhumalaŋguny.
\v 24 Ga wiripuny Mäkthu,\f * \fr 1:24 \ft Mark\f* Yaritakatjthu,\f * \fr 1:24 \ft Aristarchus\f* Dematjthu\f * \fr 1:24 \ft Demas\f* ga Lukthu,\f * \fr 1:24 \ft Luke\f* walal ga bitjandhi bili guyaŋayi nhumalany, dhuwalawurr ŋunhi napurr rrambaŋi djämamirr mala Garraywalaŋumirr.
\v 25 Ga dhuwal ŋarra ga nhinany märr-ŋamathinyamirriŋur romŋurnydja, waŋgany-manapanminyawuynha nhanukala Garraywala Djesu-Christkala.
\p Ga bilin dhuwal dhäwuny' nhuŋu. 
